Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是因为想起了祖玛的事情才抓狂的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.82,small,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰窟茑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚无瘴界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛真的很生气~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.21,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔龙吠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个咒文…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是召唤咒文！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降临吧  魔王龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔王龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊  好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.84,0:18:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃得下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方叫出那家伙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王之壶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才也说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那位娜玛的壶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么娜玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  娜玛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.32,0:19:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被转移到那副盔甲上的灵魂回到原来的身体上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么娜玛只是回到原来的身体上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  这也要看原来的身体现在在哪里和怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会在什么有生命危险的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖玛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们所持有的冥王之壶有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他持有冥王之壶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沉睡着雷藏的灵魂的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为只要跟踪着莉娜就一定能见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是花了不少时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿没有你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没有礼貌耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你认为没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不代表我也认为没有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只对她有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来勒赞迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然有人会丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人会丧命？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来勒赞迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  勒赞迪是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明弹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为我和娜玛在他计算之外所以撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总算有打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.86,0:20:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是粗野的招呼方式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上用治疗魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.44,0:21:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我也失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.02,0:21:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说让我们去勒赞迪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他手上真有冥王之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然相信你  雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这家伙会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.19,0:21:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜玛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才不会那么简单就挂掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.93,0:21:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是啊
